Class SuperPacket

java.lang.Object
com.cs309.quoridorApp.dataPackets.Packet
com.cs309.quoridorApp.dataPackets.SuperPacket
public class SuperPacket extends com.cs309.quoridorApp.dataPackets.Packet
The packet directly required by the main controllers. Used to generate sub-packets, which hold the logic and interactions for performing actions upon the server and game.
